a.org/resource/Carl_Hester\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Fry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Fry\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jake Jarman added a fourth bronze of the day in the men's gymnastics floor final before Max Whitlock slipped out of the medals after his final ever routine on the pommel horse.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_the_Dog\", \"score\": 0.9956328978389408, \"rank\": 0.002576707415418466, \"text\": \"Jake\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_the_Dog\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_the_Dog\"}, {\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Max Whitlock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Whitlock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Followi's live blog for updates.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to close this blog now after another exciting day at the Olympics, which saw Team GB pick up five medals including a gold and St Lucia's Julien Alfred win the nation's first ever gold.\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.924796888552438e-15, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1117, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Lucia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999